svg.title: Desk Texture
svg.desc: A decorative wood grain texture pattern featuring rich saddle brown tones (hex: #8B4513) as the base color. The design includes flowing curved lines in a slightly lighter brown shade (hex: #A0522D) that create an organic, wave-like pattern reminiscent of natural wood grain. These curved lines are arranged in parallel, creating a sense of depth and movement across the surface, simulating the authentic appearance of a wooden desk surface.
